ata: Handle ATA NCQ NO-DATA commands correctly

Add a new taskfile protocol ATA_PROT_NCQ_NODATA to handle
ATA NCQ NO-DATA commands correctly.
And fixup ata_scsi_zbc_out_xlat() to use it.

